<paragraph id="IFRS01_B4"><paranum>B4</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 1"/><data name="paranum" value="B4"/></prolog><body><variant base="F18893845" id="IFRS01_B4_V2">       <p outputclass="keep_with_next" id="IFRS01_P0276">As required by <xref base="F43661082" href="../ifrs09/IFRS09_TOC.dita#IFRS09_TOC0001" id="IFRS01_X0413">IFRS 9</xref>, at the <xref base="F7282728" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_P0223">date of transition to IFRSs<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0071"/></ph></xref> an entity shall:</p>              <ol base="F7282769" type="lower-alpha" id="IFRS01_L0025"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value>           <p base="F7282770" id="IFRS01_P0279">measure all derivatives at <xref base="SL7282832" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_DI0003" scope="local">fair value<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0119"/></ph></xref>; and</p>         </li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value>           <p base="F7282772" id="IFRS01_P0280">eliminate all deferred losses and gains arising on derivatives that were reported in accordance with <xref base="F7282736" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_P0239">previous GAAP<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0299"/></ph></xref> as if they were assets or liabilities.</p>                    </li></ol>     </variant></body></paragraph>